article.description: — Antavion Collum had 14 points in McNeese's 74-67 victory against Texas A&M-CC on Saturday night.

article.story: LAKE CHARLES, La. -- — Antavion Collum had 14 points in McNeese's 74-67 victory against Texas A&M-CC on Saturday night. Collum added eight rebounds for the Cowboys (21-3, 10-1 Southland Conference). Christian Shumate scored 12 points and added 13 rebounds and four blocks. Javohn Garcia had 12 points and shot 2 of 4 from the field and 7 for 8 from the line. The Islanders (14-9, 7-3) were led by Garry Clark, who posted 16 points, nine rebounds and two steals. Dayne Prim added 15 points and eight rebounds for Texas A&M-CC. In addition, Dian Wright-Forde had 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
